Usage: set_clock_transition [-help] <slew_time> <clock_list> [-fall] [-max]
                            [-min] [-rise]

-help                 # Prints out the command usage
<slew_time>           # Slew time (transition time) of the clock pins
                      # (float, required)
<clock_list>          # List of clocks only with ideal mode in the design
                      # (string, required)
-fall                 # Falling edge of the register clock pins on which the
                      # slew time is asserted (bool, optional)
-max                  # Clock slew time for maximum process corner slew time
                      # (bool, optional)
-min                  # Clock slew time for minimum process corner slew time
                      # (bool, optional)
-rise                 # Rising edge of the register clock pins on which the
                      # slew time is asserted (bool, optional)